## ⚙️ Required Dependencies

Make sure to install the following libraries before running the project with **Daphne**:

```bash
# Installs Django as the main backend framework.
pip install django

# Installs Django REST Framework for API development.
pip install djangorestframework

# Installs Django Channels to support WebSocket communication.
pip install channels

# Installs the Redis backend for Django Channels, if Redis is used as the channel layer.
pip install channels_redis

# Installs the MQTT client library used to communicate with the Mosquitto broker.
pip install paho-mqtt

# Installs Daphne as the ASGI server for Django and WebSockets.
pip install daphne
```

> 💡 `channels_redis` is required if Redis is used as the Channel Layer backend for Django Channels.

